msgstr "5.2.70"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online banking"
msgstr "Spletno bančništvo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Online banking is configured by selecting the menu entry Settings -&gt; "
"Configure Aqbanking,"
msgstr ""
"Spletno bančništvo konfigurirate z izbiro menija Nastavitve -&gt; "
"Konfiguriraj Aqbanking,"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:19 details-aqbanking.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>KMyMoney configuration menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni konfiguracije KMyMoney</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:25 details-aqbanking.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>KMyMoney configuration menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni konfiguracije KMyMoney</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item is visible after the associated KBanking plugin has been "
"activated, which can be done via the menu item &quot;Configure "
"KMyMoney&quot; and after selecting the &quot;Plugins&quot; entry in the left-"
"hand window area."
msgstr ""
"Ta element menija je viden po aktivaciji pripadajočega vtičnika KBanking, "
"kar lahko storite prek elementa menija &quot;Konfiguriraj KMyMoney&quot; in "
"po izbiri vnosa &quot;Vtičniki&quot; v levem delu okna."

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that the checkbox in front of the line with KBanking is checked."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je potrditveno polje pred vrstico s KBanking odkljukano."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aqbanking setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev Aqbanking"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you pressed the menu entry &quot;Configure Aqbanking&quot; you will "
"see the following dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete menijsko postavko &quot;Konfiguriraj Aqbanking&quot;, se bo "
"prikazalo naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding takes place in two steps. The first step is to add a user and the "
"second step is to add an account."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje poteka v dveh korakih. Prvi korak je dodajanje uporabnika, drugi "
"korak pa dodajanje računa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a user"
msgstr "Ustvari uporabnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing &quot;Create user&quot; you will be redirected to the &quot;"
"New user Wizard&quot; dialog shown below:"
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na &quot;Ustvari uporabnika&quot; boste preusmerjeni v spodaj "
"prikazano pogovorno okno &quot;Čarovnik za novega uporabnika&quot;:"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create user for HBCI"
msgstr "Ustvari uporabnika za HBCI"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:92 details-aqbanking.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select online banking protocol"
msgstr "Izberite protokol za spletno bančništvo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:93 details-aqbanking.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing &quot;Next&quot; you will see a list of available online "
"banking protocols:"
msgstr ""
"Po pritisku na &quot;Naprej&quot; boste videli seznam razpoložljivih "
"protokolov za spletno bančništvo:"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring a HBCI account"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje računa HBCI"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After choosing &quot;HBCI backend using AqHBCI&quot; and pressing &quot;"
"Next&quot; you will see the following page, on which you can select the "
"security type:"
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete &quot;Zaledje HBCI z uporabo AqHBCI&quot; in pritisnete&quot;"
"Naprej&quot;, se bo prikazala naslednja stran, na kateri lahko izberetevrsto "
"varnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <ulink url=\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/projects/aqbanking/wiki/"
"AqBanking6_Bankentabelle#section-2\">AqBanking6 Bank Table</ulink> for some "
"details on the types of security supported by banks. If your bank is not "
"listed there, you should try Pin/TAN first."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnosti o vrstah varnosti, ki jih podpirajo banke, glejte <ulink url="
"\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/projects/aqbanking/wiki/"
"AqBanking6_Bankentabelle#section-2\">Tabelo bank AqBanking6</ulink>. Če vaše "
"banke ni na seznamu, najprej poskusite s PIN/TAN."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setup pin/Tan"
msgstr "Nastavitev pin/Tan"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select bank and server url"
msgstr "Izberite banko in URL strežnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At <ulink url=\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/projects/aqbanking/wiki/"
"AqBanking6_Bankentabelle\">AqBanking6 Bankentabelle</ulink> you can find a "
"list of bank server url known to work."
msgstr ""
"Na spletni strani <ulink url=\"https://www.aquamaniac.de/rdm/projects/"
"aqbanking/wiki/AqBanking6_Bankentabelle\">AqBanking6 Bankentabelle</ulink> "
"najdete seznam URL-jev bančnih strežnikov, za katere je znano, da delujejo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select bank account and user name"
msgstr "Izberite bančni račun in uporabniško ime"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose extended settings or continue"
msgstr "Izberite razširjene nastavitve ali nadaljujte"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select extended settings"
msgstr "Izberite razširjene nastavitve"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:191 details-aqbanking.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finish creating user"
msgstr "Dokončaj ustvarjanje uporabnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing &quot;Next&quot; aqbanking will contact the server and "
"fetches the server certificate and bank info."
msgstr ""
"Po pritisku na &quot;Naprej&quot; bo aqbanking vzpostavil stik s strežnikom "
"in pridobil potrdilo strežnika ter bančne podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "After pressing &quot;Close&quot; your user account has been created."
msgstr "Po kliku na gumb &quot;Zapri&quot; je vaš uporabniški račun ustvarjen."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add account"
msgstr "Dodaj račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case that adding a user account did not fail, the accounts associated to "
"the given bank should already be present in the account list."
msgstr ""
"Če dodajanje uporabniškega računa ni bilo uspešno, bi morali biti računi, "
"povezani z dano banko, že prisotni na seznamu računov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paypal"
msgstr "Paypal"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring a user for Paypal"
msgstr "Konfiguracija uporabnika za Paypal"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After choosing &quot;Paypal&quot; and pressing &quot;Next&quot; you will see "
"the following info page:"
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete &quot;Paypal&quot; in pritisnete &quot;Naprej&quot;, se vam bo "
"prikazala naslednja stran z informacijami:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press &quot;Run&quot; to continue."
msgstr "Za nadaljevanje pritisnite &quot;Zaženi&quot;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter user name and the Paypal email address"
msgstr "Vnesite uporabniško ime in e-poštni naslov Paypala"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select API settings"
msgstr "Izberite nastavitve API-ja"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Summary info before creating the user"
msgstr "Povzetek informacij pred ustvarjanjem uporabnika"

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter new password for the Paypal user"
msgstr "Vnesite novo geslo za uporabnika Paypala"

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "After pressing &quot;finish&quot; the user account has been created."
msgstr "Po pritisku na &quot;končaj&quot; je uporabniški račun ustvarjen."

#. Tag: para
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "The remaining step is to create a new account based on this user."
msgstr "Preostali korak je ustvariti nov račun na podlagi tega uporabnika."

#. Tag: title
#: details-aqbanking.docbook:316 details-aqbanking.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add paypal account"
msgstr "Dodaj račun PayPal"
